{"tid":919830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登有愛] 今日凌晨跌左銀包","createTime":"2018-11-28T10:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T16:15:10.000Z","uid":63504,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12c3bbfe1e79e8fc943fa447eb84891d4b54143a","tid":919830,"uid":63504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:50:12.000Z","msg":"幫朋友出post，希望有心人執到見到呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日凌晨大概四點左右係的士跌左銀包<br />\n銀包個款係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aArWf3N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaArWf3N.png&h=374c1584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀包裡面有一千蚊現金<br />\n一張中銀提款卡，一張中銀公司卡<br />\n一張恆生信用卡<br />\n一張安信信用卡<br />\n一張交通銀行Visa信用卡，一張交通銀行銀聯卡<br />\n一張身分證<br />\n一張回鄉證<br />\n一張八達通<br />\n<br />\n因為工作需要唔見曬啲身分證回鄉證銀行卡好唔麻煩，重酬HKD 3000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有消息可以TG：<a href=\"https://t.me/alice0234\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Falice0234&d=fPWMuOvQh280tnIgzO8zYtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c9894441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/alice0234</a><br />\n希望連登有愛可以搵得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09471fdd39f651bedf245d5d317842b362175d0a","tid":919830,"uid":14200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:56:45.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5fabea1a688f6d2fc318e1ac921e49679982601","tid":919830,"uid":23468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/f